name: invader__________glare
description:
WHAT IS THAT?
It smells weird
It scared me
I want it to go away...

What is this place?
I've never seen it before.
But something feels familiar

Now I don't just smell it.
and I'm afraid.

The difference is marked.
It's a completely original sensation.

Did that bring it?

Everything stands out so much.
I never expected to feel something like this.

By Rotten_ttc
